{"tid":2151575,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「台灣曾經報禁37年，香港要的自由我們懂。」","createTime":"2020-08-11T12:40:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T01:27:12.000Z","uid":209657,"like":328,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"a063b87a20c760fd5e0a63ee656efc0c608d6b73","tid":2151575,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T12:40:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/117195963_3182253085187939_6720918776583575596_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_sid=8bfeb9&amp;_nc_ohc=FYlnLSmpARMAX-Gkj49&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=0adc4bc7a8ea47c97a0b24202bad2652&amp;oe=5F57C0A8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F117195963_3182253085187939_6720918776583575596_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_sid%3D8bfeb9%26_nc_ohc%3DFYlnLSmpARMAX-Gkj49%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26oh%3D0adc4bc7a8ea47c97a0b24202bad2652%26oe%3D5F57C0A8&h=00148d65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【珍惜自由，致敬報業從業人員】<br />\n<br />\n臺灣已經走過報禁超過30年。<br />\n<br />\n戒嚴時期，政府在1951年開始實施對報紙出版的限制。包括禁止新報紙的登記、限制一份報紙的張數、限制印刷廠的地點。<br />\n<br />\n一直到報禁解除的1988年，長達37年的時間，我們只能有31家報紙、每份只能有3大張的內容、距離業者登記地較遠的地方甚至要到下午才能取得當天的報紙。"},{"pid":"3a0f3bf5faec379ffbb956fb4b688cb18dcb5240","tid":2151575,"uid":209657,"like":75,"dislike":1,"score":74,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T12:41:03.000Z","msg":"即便如此，仍有許許多多的人想要突破這些限制，戮力追求思想及言論的自由。<br />\n<br />\n從戒嚴時期的醞釀、經過報禁解除後的百花齊放，到讀報量年年下降的現在，面臨數位化、網路時代等各種挑戰，走過數次興衰，仍日日夜夜、不間斷地產出。<br />\n<br />\n因此，無論社會如何變動，隔天一早走進便利商店，總能看見不同立場、不同聲音的報紙同步出現，不曾噤聲。<br />\n<br />\n沒有報禁的日子，總有一天會多過不自由的日子。我們會漸漸習慣自由的空氣，但不能忘記自由其實得來不易。<br />\n<br />\n而報業從業人員，身在守護自由發聲管道的最前線，我們充滿敬意、珍惜並感謝。"},{"pid":"5788e09a63508a174fa1483d9415a38d03720257","tid":2151575,"uid":209657,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T12:42:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/www.moc.gov.tw/photos/a.656283814451558/3182253081854606/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwww.moc.gov.tw%2Fphotos%2Fa.656283814451558%2F3182253081854606%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9Fm8KfKULefuOMk0AcQ9dAAw%3D&h=7174ecbe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/www.moc.gov.tw/photos/a.656283814451558/3182253081854606/?type=3</a>"},{"pid":"cbf36336e47fb87c9246a206b84c552b7c6749e4","tid":2151575,"uid":209657,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T12:44:26.000Z","msg":"謝謝臺灣文化部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0a3a793698b55ff8fcd8f45a6b80a08c318008c","tid":2151575,"uid":337052,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T12:46:43.000Z","msg":"向黨外雜誌時期的台灣民主致敬！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.peoplenews.tw/news/75ad2be8-5226-4808-8001-ae2401424b2e\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.peoplenews.tw%2Fnews%2F75ad2be8-5226-4808-8001-ae2401424b2e&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9Fm8KfKULefuOMk0AcQ9dAAw%3D&h=6414dd73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.peoplenews.tw/news/75ad2be8-5226-4808-8001-ae2401424b2e</a>"},{"pid":"7e96e16485c7e2cdd1a35b50cfc5b8e2a6b10f68","tid":2151575,"uid":198,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T12:48:01.000Z","msg":"可以講多個故事 宜家奶共奶到發發聲既中時 黨禁時候係最反共同最爭取自由 不過可惜個仔做唔掂賣左盤俾旺旺"},{"pid":"eb5ec8aa06bf333f05e003560cba0bbd6f0b7b4a","tid":2151575,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0a3a793698b55ff8fcd8f45a6b80a08c318008c","tid":2151575,"uid":337052,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T12:46:43.000Z","msg":"向黨外雜誌時期的台灣民主致敬！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.peoplenews.tw/news/75ad2be8-5226-4808-8001-ae2401424b2e\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.peoplenews.tw%2Fnews%2F75ad2be8-5226-4808-8001-ae2401424b2e&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9Fm8KfKULefuOMk0AcQ9dAAw%3D&h=6414dd73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.peoplenews.tw/news/75ad2be8-5226-4808-8001-ae2401424b2e</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20